<li>Update the code to validate the returned upgrade url so as to ensure that we only offer to upgrade to builds that exist.</li>

</ul>



<h4>0.5</h4>



<ul>

<li>Initial Release containing support for switching your blog to point release nightlies or bleeding edge nightlies</li>

</ul>";}s:17:"short_description";s:46:"Allows you to easily upgrade to Beta releases.";s:13:"download_link";s:68:"http://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wordpress-beta-tester.0.96.zip";s:4:"tags";a:3:{s:8:"advanced";s:8:"advanced";s:4:"beta";s:4:"beta";s:7:"testing";s:7:"testing";}}','autoload' => 'no'),
